* Title      : NeoWidEx
* Written by : Tom Stepleton
* Date       : XX November 2016
* Description:
*   Formatting and diagnostic tool for Widget drives,
*   inspired by the WidEx utility internal to Apple, and by
*   Patrick Sch√§fer's UsbWidEx hardware tool.
